+ Base Class

The [Solar_Base::HomePage Solar_Base] class is a lightweight base class from which all other Solar classes descend (not including exceptions, which descend from [Solar_Exception::HomePage Solar_Exception]).  This base class provides:

||~ Description ||~ See Also ||
|| A standard constructor that reads from the ConfigFile then combines the instantiation-time ConstructorParameters with the default property values for the class. || Solar_Base::__construct() ||
|| A single property to collect configuration values for the class and its parents. || Solar_Base::$_config ||
|| A method for finding and returning exceptions with localized message text. || Solar_Base::_exception() ||
|| A method for finding and returning localized text strings. || Solar_Base::locale() ||
|| A method for finding the API version of the class. || Solar_Base::apiVersion() ||
